# Sensei — environment configuration
#
# The app is CLIENT-ONLY today (seed data + localStorage). The canonical API
# client in src/services/ is DORMANT until you point it at a backend by setting
# the base URL below. With it unset, nothing calls the backend and all current
# flows work unchanged.
#
# Only client-safe (VITE_-prefixed) values may live here — Vite inlines them into
# the browser bundle. NEVER put secrets, JWT signing keys, or database URLs in a
# VITE_ variable; those belong to the backend and its host secret store.

# Backend base URL. When set, src/services/apiClient.ts becomes active.
# Example: https://api.sensei.example.com
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
